{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你难道也要教奸人得意了么？","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":2,"line_end":2},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"裴大先生，你怎的如此软弱，被人如此欺负了，还不敢动手，难道你也怕了他们么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":6,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_hu","speaker_name":"东方湖","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"有这许多藏头露尾，见不得人的鼠辈在为你呐喊，你还怕谁？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":49,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_guan_er","speaker_name":"管二","listener":"char_dong_fang_tie","text":"大公子，二公子，是这个在这里乱叫，快——","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_tie","speaker_name":"东方铁","listener":null,"text":"管二！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":49,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_tie","speaker_name":"东方铁","listener":"char_dong_fang_zhen","text":"有五弟一人去追足够了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":28,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jiang","speaker_name":"东方江","listener":null,"text":"若是捉住了那人，我倒要看看他究竟是什么变的？","tone":"厉声","chapter":49,"line_start":32,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jian","speaker_name":"东方剑","listener":null,"text":"管二？是管二么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":49,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_tie","speaker_name":"东方铁","listener":null,"text":"果然是管二，他必定是发现了呼喊之人，想不到却遭了那人的毒手。","tone":"无奈","chapter":49,"line_start":44,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jiang","speaker_name":"东方江","listener":"char_dong_fang_hu","text":"凶手呢？","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_zhen","speaker_name":"东方震","listener":"char_dong_fang_jiang","text":"此时此地，便有一千个凶手也尽可在人丛中隐藏起来。","tone":"淡然","chapter":49,"line_start":52,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_dong_fang_hu","text":"这算什么？","tone":"严肃","chapter":49,"line_start":58,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_hu","speaker