{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jian","speaker_name":"东方剑","listener":null,"text":"是谁？","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":110,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_tie","speaker_name":"东方铁","listener":null,"text":"是哪位前辈高人光临此间，不妨……","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":114,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_shen_mi_gao_shou","speaker_name":"神秘高手","listener":null,"text":"不分是谁，不查究竟，委实昏庸愚蠢之极，我且将那些呐喊之人抓来给你，让你看看他们究竟是何人的手下？","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":118,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"黑衣大汉","listener":"char_dong_fang_tie","text":"饶命……小人没有说什么？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":49,"line_start":136,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jiang","speaker_name":"东方江","listener":"char_hei_yi_da_han","text":"你是谁的门下，受了谁的指使？在我数到三字以前，快些与我乖乖说出来，否则我就刺穿你的琵琶双骨，刺瞎你的一双眼睛。","tone":"厉声","chapter":49,"line_start":142,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_jiang","speaker_name":"东方江","listener":"char_hei_yi_da_han","text":"一！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":49,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"黑衣大汉","listener":"char_dong_fang_jiang","text":"小人没有……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":49,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_dong_fang_hu","speaker_name":"东方湖","listener":"char_hei_yi_da_han","text":"二！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":49,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"黑衣大汉","listener":"char_dong_fang_jiang","text":"我说，我说……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":49,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"黑衣大汉","listener":"char_dong_fang_jiang","text":"小人……小人是七巧山庄，那庄主的手下。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":49,"line_start":160,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"原来是七巧追魂的手下！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":49,"line_start":164,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":null,"text":"一石四鸟，伤人无形，嘿嘿，好厉害的连环毒计！","tone":"冷笑","chapter":49,"line_