{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":294,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"裴珏在这里么？裴珏你在哪里？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":210,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"向帮主别来无恙，有何见教！","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你还认得我么？","tone":"厉声","chapter":49,"line_start":220,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你还记得你是如何登上江南同盟盟主宝座的么？想不到你此刻竟真的作威作福了起来。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":224,"line_end":228},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"向帮主自管请便，在下恕不奉陪了！","tone":"淡然","chapter":49,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你想走么？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":232,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"我走不得么？","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你要走也行，不过我先要问你，我手下的鸡冠包晓天，究竟犯下了什么大罪，你要将他置之死地！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":238,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"包晓天已死了么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":49,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"不错，他已被你假借江南同盟的帮助，杀死在伏牛山的荒郊，若非我发现得早，他尸身都要被蛇兽所噬——","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":246,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"在他身旁是否还有那黑驴追风的尸身？","tone":"疑问","chapter":49,"line_start":250,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你既然知道，若不与我说个明白，今日就叫你为他偿命！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":254,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":null,"text":"想不到神手战飞毕竟还是将他们杀死了！","tone":"无奈","chapter":49,"line_start":260,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"你想将罪过推在战飞身上么？你以为我还怕了战飞不成？我今日先宰了你，再找战飞算账！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":264,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_pei_jue","speaker_name":"裴珏","listener":"char_xiang_yi_ti","text":"你疯了么？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_xiang_yi_ti","speaker_name":"向一啼","listener":"char_pei_jue","text":"不管我是否疯了，今日也要你来与包晓天纳命！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":49,"line_start":276,"line_end":278}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_yi_ti","name":"向一啼","alias":["金鸡"],"identity":"金鸡帮帮主","faction":"金鸡帮","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"金鸡帮帮主，性情刚烈，为手下兄弟不惜拼命","personality":{"traits":["刚烈","重义","暴躁","血性","直率"],"speech_style":"厉声大喝","temperament":"暴烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_pei_jue","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"寻仇对峙"},{"target":"char_bao_xiao_tian","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"为手下报仇"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":212,"line_end":212,"text":"走出一个手握铁拐，满面怒容的汉子，竟正是那武林金鸡帮之首，金鸡向一啼"}]},{"id":"char_bao_xiao_tian","name":"包晓天","alias":["鸡冠"],"identity":"金鸡帮鸡冠","faction":"金鸡帮","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"金鸡帮鸡冠，被杀于伏牛山荒郊","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","勇猛","义气","直率","鲁莽"],"speech_style":"豪爽","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_yi_ti","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"忠诚手下"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":240,"line_end":242,"text":"我手下的鸡冠包晓天，究竟犯下了什么大罪"}]},{"id":"char_hei_lui_zhui_feng","name":"黑驴追风","alias":[],"identity":"江湖人物","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"与包晓天一同